name: frida-agent-example
description: Example Frida agent written in TypeScript

scripts.f: npm run build && cross-env-shell frida $npm_package_config_connect -l _agent.js -f $npm_package_config_app -o current.log
scripts.F: npm run build && cross-env-shell frida $npm_package_config_connect -l _agent.js -F $npm_package_config_app -o current.log
scripts.a: npm run build && cross-env-shell frida $npm_package_config_connect -l _agent.js $npm_package_config_app -o current.log
scripts.p: npm run build && cross-env-shell frida $npm_package_config_connect -l _agent.js  -o current.log -p
scripts.d: npm run build && cross-env-shell frida $npm_package_config_connect -l _agent.js --debug --runtime=v8 -F $npm_package_config_app  -o current.log
